<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٨١ سورة التكوير]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>[سورة التكوير <span class="c2">(٨١)</span> : الآيات ١ الى ٩]<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>إِذَا الشَّمْسُ كُوِّرَتْ <span class="c2">(١)</span> وَإِذَا النُّجُومُ انْكَدَرَتْ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَإِذَا الْجِبالُ سُيِّرَتْ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> وَإِذَا الْعِشارُ عُطِّلَتْ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَإِذَا الْوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتْ <span class="c2">(٥)</span> وَإِذَا الْبِحارُ سُجِّرَتْ <span class="c2">(٦)</span> وَإِذَا النُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتْ <span class="c2">(٧)</span> وَإِذَا الْمَوْؤُدَةُ سُئِلَتْ <span class="c2">(٨)</span> بِأَيِّ ذَنْبٍ قُتِلَتْ <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١-<span class="c5"> إِذَا الشَّمْسُ كُوِّرَتْ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>كُوِّرَتْ لفت ومحى ضوؤها.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٢-<span class="c5"> وَإِذَا النُّجُومُ انْكَدَرَتْ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>انْكَدَرَتْ انطمس نورها، وتساقطت.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٣-<span class="c5"> وَإِذَا الْجِبالُ سُيِّرَتْ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>سُيِّرَتْ حركت من أماكنها.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٤-<span class="c5"> وَإِذَا الْعِشارُ عُطِّلَتْ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>الْعِشارُ ما من شأنه أن يحمل.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>عُطِّلَتْ فقد خاصته.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٥-<span class="c5"> وَإِذَا الْوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتْ:</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>حُشِرَتْ جمعت فى أوكارها وأجحارها ذاهلة من شدة الفزع.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٦-<span class="c5"> وَإِذَا الْبِحارُ سُجِّرَتْ:</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>سُجِّرَتْ تأججت نارا.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>٧-<span class="c5"> وَإِذَا النُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتْ:</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>النُّفُوسُ الأزواج.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>زُوِّجَتْ قرنت بأجسادها.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>٨-<span class="c5"> وَإِذَا الْمَوْؤُدَةُ سُئِلَتْ:</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>الْمَوْؤُدَةُ التي دفنت حية.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>سُئِلَتْ ترضية لها وسخطا على من وأدها.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>٩-<span class="c5"> بِأَيِّ ذَنْبٍ قُتِلَتْ:</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>